<i>♪ And we are jumping
Shoo-bee-doo-bee-doo ♪</i>

1514
01:19:44,469 --> 01:19:48,240
<i>♪ And we are singing
'Til the morning comes around ♪</i>

1515
01:19:48,941 --> 01:19:53,010
<i>♪ How I wish this party night
