1516
01:19:53,012 --> 01:19:54,510
<i>♪ When we see the sunrise ♪</i>

1517
01:19:54,512 --> 01:19:56,747
<i>♪ We will say
"Goodbye, my friend" ♪</i>

1518
01:19:56,749 --> 01:20:00,716
<i>♪ But right now, we're dancing
